h3. Problema
Ensure the contrast between foreground and background colors meets WCAG 2 AA minimum contrast ratio thresholds

h3. Criterio WCAG
1.4.3

h3. Approccio Remediation
https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/4.10/color-contrast?application=webdriverjs

h3. Esempio Codice
{code}

/* PRIMA (Contrasto insufficiente) */
.text {
    color: #999999;
    background: #ffffff;
}

/* DOPO (Contrasto corretto 4.5:1) */
.text {
    color: #595959;
    background: #ffffff;
}

{code}

h3. Testing
Verificare contrasto con Color Contrast Analyzer (minimo 4.5:1)

